article.description: — Marques Warrick scored 28 points as Northern Kentucky beat Robert Morris 70-60 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Warrick scores 28, Northern Kentucky takes down Robert Morris 70-60
article.linkText: Warrick scores 28, Northern Kentucky takes down Robert Morris 70-60
article.story: MOON TOWNSHIP, Pa. -- — Marques Warrick scored 28 points as Northern Kentucky beat Robert Morris 70-60 on Wednesday night. Warrick added five assists for the Norse (17-13, 12-7 Horizon League). Trey Robinson scored 18 points and added five rebounds and three steals. Michael Bradley finished 4 of 9 from 3-point range and 3 for 3 from the line to finish with 15 points. Josh Corbin led the way for the Colonials (10-20, 6-13) with 14 points. TJ Wainwright added 12 points and four assists for Robert Morris. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
